# Project

Manages a [Project](https://www.palantir.com/docs/foundry/security/projects-and-roles/).
The following operations are currently supported:

- Create a Project
- Update a Project
- Delete a Project
- Import a Project

This resource respects the `delete_mode` provider-level flag.

